_sText:
I always loved to_trooper when I was playing Tactical Ops, long time ago.

So I decided to give it a try, designing this map for Counter-Strike: Source.
Its a Bomb/defuse map.

I tried to contact Peter Andries who has made the original for Tactical Ops but since today I didnt get an answer so I just can hope that its good enough and you guys like it.

Hope you Enjoy!
